items.name: Artisan Coffee House
items.description: Specialty coffee shop featuring single-origin beans and house-made pastries. Cozy atmosphere with plenty of seating for work or conversation.

items.name: Book & Brew
items.description: Combination bookstore and café with a large selection of books and comfortable reading nooks. Serves organic coffee and tea along with light meals.

items.name: Garden Café
items.description: Café set in a beautiful garden setting with outdoor seating. Farm-to-table breakfast and lunch options with a focus on fresh, seasonal ingredients.
